external_knowledge:
- 'voyagers' refers to the users;
- 'sailed through the cinematic seas' refers to users who have reviewed movies;
- 'kept their anchors away from the shores of television' means these users have not reviewed any TV shows.

- 'gardeners' refers to the users;
- 'flower beds' metaphorically refers to tags;
- 'opened their flower beds to the public gaze' means having public tags (is_public = 1).

sql:
